name: Gleamchortle, the Crystalline MirthFlamingo
text: Beneath a cloak of darkness, Gleamchortle's silhouette flickered against flowing magma. Each chortle sparked a flare, casting light on awestruck onlookers. Far above, Glimmergiggle's luminous shadow crossed the moon, their connected spirits dancing across elements: one airy light, the other earthbound fire, both alight with playful brilliance.
